Thoughts from this extended #EV #Roadtrip, Boston to Mpls 1/

- Budget extra time for the unexpected
- Try to have backup chargers or some extra charge in case
- Using the proprietary charger app is usually best.
- Consider setting  up charger accounts + order cards ahead of time

Thoughts from this extended #EV #Roadtrip, Boston to Mpls 2/

- Driving of an EV is less taxing on road trips
- You may spend 20-30 min at a high speed charger at a mall, rest stop, or downtown.
- Plan what to do during charging: Run, read a book, explore, nap, meal, etc.
